sición de HyQvia, su falta de comprensión de conceptos clave como la función de la rHuPH20 y la variabilidad pico-valle limita su puntuación.  El puntaje refleja la necesidad de un refuerzo significativo en su conocimiento del producto.\r\n<br><br><br>',	27,	'2025-08-26 05:10:03',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	0,	0),
(164,	'xo49d3JsXy5L2RZ0jSVFhCrD7imYgOzl6feawNHq',	NULL,	4,	3,	'sitepal-avatar-female-11.jpg',	NULL,	'<b>Overall Assessment</b>:  The user, four, demonstrated a foundational level of understanding of ADAS during the session. They were not familiar with the specific functionalities and limitations of systems like ACC, LKAS, and AEB initially, but showed a willingness to learn and understand the explanations provided.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Strengths</b>: The user\'s main strength lies in their openness to learning and ability to acknowledge gaps in their knowledge. They actively engaged in the conversation by asking for clarifications and expressing gratitude for the explanations given.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Weaknesses: </b>: The user initially lacked knowledge about the basic functions and limitations of key ADAS technologies such as ACC, LKAS, and AEB. They required detailed explanations for each system, indicating a need for foundational knowledge in ADAS.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Recommendations</b>:  It is recommended that the user begins with a basic course or reading material on ADAS to build a solid foundation. Engaging in more interactive sessions like quizzes or practical demonstrations could also enhance their understanding and retention of the functionalities and limitations of various ADAS technologies.\r\n<br>\r\n \r\n<br><br><br>',	NULL,	'2025-08-26 06:57:08',	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	0,	0),
