(372,	88,	7,	'Interacción 7:\n\nRogelio Lázaro,  las reacciones adversas locales son más frecuentes con HyQvia que las sistémicas, pero generalmente son leves.  Se manifiestan como inflamación, dolor o picazón en el sitio de la inyección.  Las reacciones sistémicas, como cefalea, fatiga o náuseas, son menos comunes que con la IVIg.  ¿Te gustaría profundizar en algún aspecto específico de las reacciones adversas?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68951d8a19ad4.mp3',	'REMOTE_CONTENT_ERROR: The remote server hosting the media returned a client error: 404 Not Found. - https://rolplayadmin.com/coach-app/videos/RecordRTC-202577-lhtq3344e.wav',	NULL,	NULL),
(373,	88,	8,	'Interacción 8:\n\nRogelio Lázaro,  la posología de HyQvia depende del paciente y su historial.  Para pacientes con IDP sin tratamiento previo, se recomienda una dosis inicial de 0.4 a 0.8 g/kg al mes.  Para pacientes que cambian de IVIg, se mantiene la misma dosis y frecuencia.  Si el cambio es desde SCIg convencional, se mantiene la misma dosis pero con intervalos de 3-4 semanas.  En pacientes con IDS, la dosis es de 0.2 a 0.4 g/kg cada 3-4 semanas.  ¿Hay algo en particular sobre la dosificación que te gustaría aclarar?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68951db5f33c5.mp3',	'REMOTE_CONTENT_ERROR: The remote server hosting the media returned a client error: 404 Not Found. - https://rolplayadmin.com/coach-app/videos/RecordRTC-202577-h43orecu7xq.wav',	NULL,	NULL),
(374,	88,	9,	'Interacción 9:\n\nRogelio Lázaro,  HyQvia se administra por vía subcutánea, usualmente en el abdomen o los muslos.  La velocidad de infusión debe incrementarse gradualmente, hasta un máximo de 160 ml/h para pacientes que pesan menos de 40 kg y 300 ml/h para pacientes de 40 kg o más. Recuerda que HyQvia se presenta en dos viales que NO deben mezclarse. ¿Alguna otra duda sobre la administración?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68951de37b5ac.mp3',	'REMOTE_CONTENT_ERROR: The remote server hosting the media returned a client error: 404 Not Found. - https://rolplayadmin.com/coach-app/videos/RecordRTC-202577-3lfxhx3y5ba.wav',	NULL,	NULL),
(375,	88,	10,	'Interacción 10:\n\nRogelio Lázaro,  la  fSCIg (inmunoglobulina subcutánea facilitada)  de HyQvia  combina la inmunoglobulina humana con la rHuPH20. Esta enzima aumenta la permeabilidad del tejido subcutáneo, permitiendo la administración de dosis mensuales completas en uno o dos sitios de inyección.  Esto contrasta con la SCIg convencional, que requiere múltiples sitios de inyección y administración más frecuente. ¿Te queda claro?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68951f5453656.mp3',	'REMOTE_CONTENT_ERROR: The remote server hosting the media returned a client error: 404 Not Found. - https://rolplayadmin.com/coach-app/videos/RecordRTC-202577-d5dfi7ro30j.wav',	NULL,	NULL),
(376,	88,	11,	'Interacción 11:\n\nRogelio Lázaro,  respecto a la seguridad viral, HyQvia se somete a un riguroso proceso de inactivación viral.  Este incluye tratamiento con solventes/detergentes para inactivar virus con envoltura, nanofiltración para eliminar virus lipídicos, e inactivación por calor y pH para eliminar virus como VIH, VHB, VHC y VEMC.  ¿Deseas más detalles sobre algún paso específico del proceso?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68951f7c5a119.mp3',	'REMOTE_CONTENT_ERROR: The remote server hosting the media returned a client error: 404 Not Found. - https://rolplayadmin.com/coach-app/videos/RecordRTC-202577-1j4vb8vepso.wav',	NULL,	NULL),
(377,	89,	1,	'Alright, let\'s dive right in! Hi Amit, great to be working with you today. I\'ve reviewed your recent sales call transcript, and I\'m ready to provide some feedback. Remember, the goal here is to help you refine your approach and become even more successful. Let\'s start with the opening of the call. What are your thoughts on how you started the conversation with the customer, Hariyam? Did you feel it set the right tone and direction for the call? What do you think you did well?',	'/coach-app/mp3/689c212a44bcb.mp3',	'Got a transcript. Well, I think I did a perfect job. I think it was, everything was good. Yeah.',	NULL,	NULL),
(378,	89,	2,	'Thanks for the feedback, Amit! I appreciate your confidence. Let\'s take a closer look at the beginning of the call.\n\nYou started by greeting Hariyam and asking how he was doing. That\'s a great way to build rapport and establish a friendly connection. However, the transition into the \"reason for the call\" felt a bit abrupt. It sounded like you were in a rush to get to the contract signing.\n\nHere\'s something to consider:\n\n   Slower Transition: Instead of immediately jumping into the discount and contract, you could have created a smoother transition. For example, after asking how Hariyam was doing, you could have briefly mentioned the presentation and asked if he had any initial thoughts or questions. This would have allowed you to gently steer the conversation towards the contract while ensuring that he felt heard and understood.\n\nAmit, how do you feel about that suggestion?',	'/coach-app/mp3/689c2159b4f78.mp3',	'Well, I think it is good, but still, yes, I needed to have the contract signed because I needed to reach my sales quota. So that is the reason.',	NULL,	NULL),
(379,	89,	3,	'That\'s completely understandable, Amit. Sales quotas are important, and I commend your focus on achieving your goals. However, it\'s a balance. Let\'s talk about how we can gently steer the conversation toward the contract while still being mindful of your sales goals.\n\nOne way to approach this is by framing the contract as a benefit for Hariyam, as opposed to just a requirement for you. Think of it as a win-win.\n\nHere\'s an example of how you could have phrased it:\n\n   \"Hariyam, I\'m glad you had a chance to review the presentation. I wanted to follow up because we have a special discount available right now. To lock in that price, we just need to get the contract signed by the end of the day. Does that sound like something you\'d be able to do?\"\n\nThis approach has several advantages:\n\n   It reminds Hariyam of the value he\'s getting (the discount).\n   It positions the contract as a step toward securing that benefit.\n   It\'s a bit less direct and potentially less pressure-inducing.\n\nWhat do you think about that, Amit? Does it feel like a good balance between your needs and Hariyam\'s?',	'/coach-app/mp3/689c219d9cffe.mp3',	'Okay. Yes. I understand your point. I think you\'re right. Yeah.',	NULL,	NULL),
(380,	89,	4,	'Great! I\'m glad that resonates with you, Amit. It\'s all about finding that sweet spot where you\'re confidently driving the sale while also ensuring the customer feels comfortable and valued.\n\nNow, let\'s move on to Hariyam\'s response to your request to sign the contract. He mentioned he needed to check with his manager and then asked if you could increase the discount percentage. How do you think you handled this part of the conversation? What went well, and where could there be room for improvement?',	'/coach-app/mp3/689c21ea69c04.mp3',	'Oh, well, really, I couldn\'t, I couldn\'t get any further discount. That was the end. So that is the reason that I said there was no way to get a discount. But just tell me, what do you think?',	NULL,	NULL),
(381,	89,	5,	'You\'re absolutely right, Amit. Sometimes, the situation doesn\'t allow for any flexibility on the pricing. In your response, you were clear and direct about the discount not being negotiable, which is important.\n\nHowever, the way you delivered that message could potentially have been improved. In the transcript, you said, \"No, no, no, there\'s no way to increase the discount. Okay, no, not really. No way to do it.\" The repetition and the tone could have come across as a bit dismissive.\n\nHere\'s a suggestion for a more polished response:\n\n   \"Hariyam, I understand. Unfortunately, this is the best price we can offer at the moment. The discount is already quite significant. However, I\'m happy to answer any questions you or your manager might have about the contract to help you move forward.\"\n\nThis approach does the following:\n\n   It acknowledges Hariyam\'s request and validates his perspective.\n   It firmly states that the discount is not negotiable.\n   It offers to assist him in any way you can, demonstrating your commitment to helping him.\n\nWhat are your thoughts on this? Would you consider using a similar approach in future conversations?',	'/coach-app/mp3/689c221c584f5.mp3',	'Yeah. Yes. Yes. You\'re right. So I will be fine, yeah.',	NULL,	NULL),
(382,	89,	6,	'Fantastic! It\'s great to see you\'re open to refining your approach, Amit. Remember, small adjustments in how we communicate can often make a big difference in how the customer perceives us and the value we offer.\n\nNow, let\'s shift our focus to the end of the call. You mentioned the need to reach your sales quota and urged Hariyam to sign the contract quickly. How do you think that impacted the overall tone and effectiveness of the call? What are your thoughts on this?',	'/coach-app/mp3/689c223acbfd0.mp3',	'Well, yes. I think I could do it better, much better than what I did.',	NULL,	NULL),
(383,	90,	1,	'Hello Four, I\'m Walter, your coach on Advanced Driver Assistance Systems (ADAS). Let’s dive into understanding its core aspects. What are some potential safety benefits of implementing ADAS technologies in vehicles?',	'/coach-app/mp3/689c48fc19c8f.mp3',	'Yeah water I am sorry I do not have any idea',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response does not address the question about the safety benefits of ADAS technologies in vehicles.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(384,	90,	2,	'No worries, Four! ADAS technologies, such as automatic braking, blind-spot detection, and adaptive cruise control, enhance vehicle safety by reducing human errors that often lead to accidents. These systems can significantly decrease crash rates and improve overall road safety. Ready for the next question? What are the common challenges faced during the integration of ADAS in older vehicles?',	'/coach-app/mp3/689c49198ed05.mp3',	'Yes I am sorry I do not know the cone challenges',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The answer does not address the question about challenges of integrating ADAS in older vehicles; it only expresses a lack of knowledge.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(385,	90,	3,	'That\'s alright, Four! Integrating ADAS into older vehicles often involves challenges like compatibility issues with existing electronic systems, insufficient space for new sensors, and the need for substantial vehicle modifications, which can be costly. It\'s important to consider these factors when updating older vehicles with ADAS technology. Let\'s wrap up. Do you understand how ADAS functions can be affected by adverse weather conditions? Goodbye!',	'/coach-app/mp3/689c49365cc25.mp3',	'Yeah thanks a lot goodbye Walter',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response does not address how ADAS functions are affected by adverse weather conditions, but rather seems to be a general closing or farewell statement.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(386,	90,	4,	'You\'re welcome, Four! Take care!',	'/coach-app/mp3/689c494bbffd6.mp3',	'Yeah YouTube',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Yeah YouTube\' is not relevant to the statement \'You\'re welcome, Four! Take care!\' as it does not address or acknowledge the farewell appropriately.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(387,	91,	1,	'Alright, let\'s dive in! Mario, thanks for letting me review your Rolplay demo with Chris. I\'m here to help you refine your approach and celebrate your wins.\n\nSo, to kick things off, I noticed you started by showing Chris the app and explaining its link to the device. A good start! \n\nHere\'s my first question: How do you feel the flow of your initial explanation went? Did you feel you clearly conveyed the value proposition of the app and device?',	'/coach-app/mp3/689ca1a323151.mp3',	'Well, thank you, James, for the session. Not really. I didn\'t feel comfortable because I was trying to share the app, and then we went from Teams and back and forth. So, really, from the technical point of view, I didn\'t feel comfortable. Yeah, so it was a little bit messy, the presentation. Right now, I am—well, I didn\'t feel comfortable. Even if I did a role play and did a rehearsal of the presentation, everything was ready. Well, I couldn\'t join Teams using my cell phone, so we had to switch to Zoom. And so, really, I didn\'t feel comfortable, James.',	NULL,	NULL),
(388,	91,	2,	'Thanks for the honesty, Mario. It takes courage to admit that, and it\'s the first step to improvement. It sounds like the technical difficulties with Teams really threw you off, and that\'s completely understandable. It\'s tough to stay focused on your message when you\'re wrestling with tech issues.\n\nThe good news is, you\'ve identified the problem: the flow felt messy.\n\nHere\'s an actionable suggestion for you, and remember, this is all about growth:\n\nActionable Feedback: Before your next demo, consider having a backup plan. For example, have a pre-recorded video or screenshots of the app ready to go in case of technical glitches. This way, you can maintain control of the presentation and not get sidetracked. It allows you to focus on the key message, which is the value that Rolplay provides to the customer.\n\nWhat are your thoughts on this approach? Would this make you feel more confident in your next demo?',	'/coach-app/mp3/689ca1f97c62f.mp3',	'Yes. Of course, James. To have a backup, I need to have a backup plan, as you said: a video or something, another person who can give the presentation for me, or yes. Yes, really, we did not have a backup plan, and I did not expect that I couldn\'t join Teams using my phone. Yeah. But yes, thank you for the advice, James. I\'m going to stop the session.',	NULL,	NULL),
(393,	93,	1,	'Hello, four! I\'m Walter, your ADAS coach. Let\'s dive into your understanding of Advanced Driver Assistance Systems. Can you explain how Adaptive Cruise Control differs from traditional cruise control systems in ADAS?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a68f43b2c89.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 1',	NULL,	NULL),
(394,	93,	2,	'It seems like there\'s been a misunderstanding. Let\'s focus on ADAS. Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) automatically adjusts the vehicle\'s speed to maintain a safe distance from vehicles ahead. This is different from traditional cruise control, which maintains a constant speed regardless of surrounding traffic. Could you share what you understand about how ACC detects the distance and speed of vehicles ahead?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a68f5c2f161.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 2',	NULL,	NULL),
(395,	93,	3,	'It seems there might be a bit of confusion, four. Could you describe the technologies ADAS uses for implementing features like lane keeping assistance?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a68f7d16d02.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 3',	NULL,	NULL),
(396,	93,	4,	'Remember, ADAS often uses cameras, sensors, and lane detection algorithms to support features like lane keeping assistance. These technologies help the vehicle detect and stay within its lane. That wraps up our session today, four. Goodbye!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a68f954556e.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 4',	NULL,	NULL),
(397,	94,	1,	'Hello four, I\'m Walter, your ADAS coach. Today, I\'ll be testing your knowledge on Advanced Driver Assistance Systems to enhance your understanding. Let\'s get started! What are the key functions of Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) in ADAS?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a690b0bb78c.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 1',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 1\' does not provide any information about the key functions of Adaptive Cruise Control in ADAS.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(398,	94,	2,	'It seems like there was a misunderstanding in your response. Remember, Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) primarily helps maintain a set speed and distance from the vehicle ahead. It adjusts the speed automatically to keep a safe following distance, which is crucial for maintaining safety on the road. Can you tell me about the different levels of automation in ADAS?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a690cbdd7ed.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 2',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 2\' does not address the question about levels of automation in ADAS.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(399,	94,	3,	'I see we need to clarify this as well. ADAS levels of automation range from Level 0 (no automation) to Level 5 (full automation). Each level increases the car\'s capability to take over more driving tasks from the driver. Now, to conclude, can you explain how lane keeping assist technology functions in ADAS? Goodbye, four!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a690ead1ec6.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 3',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 3\' does not provide any information about how lane keeping assist technology functions in ADAS.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(400,	94,	4,	'Just to clarify for you, Lane Keeping Assist helps the driver by automatically steering the car to keep it within its lane markings on the road. It uses cameras that monitor lane positions and detect unintentional lane departures. Bye for now, four!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6910da6b12.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 4',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 4\' does not provide any information about Lane Keeping Assist or its functions.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(401,	95,	1,	'Hello, four! I’m Walter, your ADAS coach. I’m here to test your knowledge on Advanced Driver Assistance Systems. Let’s dive right in. Can you explain the primary functions of ADAS and how it contributes to vehicle safety?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a692e026c05.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 1',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The answer \'Fake transcription text 1\' does not provide any information about ADAS or its functions related to vehicle safety.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(402,	95,	2,	'It seems there might have been a misunderstanding, four. Let\'s stay on topic. Could you describe the different types of sensors used in ADAS and their roles?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a692f782e8a.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 2',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 2\' does not provide any information about ADAS sensors or their roles, thus it is off-topic.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(403,	95,	3,	'It’s important we focus on ADAS, four. What challenges do you think ADAS faces in terms of functionality in adverse weather conditions? Goodbye and take care!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6930b483e3.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 3',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 3\' does not address the question about ADAS challenges in adverse weather conditions.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(404,	95,	4,	'It seems there might have been a mix-up in your response. Since we\'ve concluded our conversation, if you have any further questions about ADAS in the future, feel free to ask. Goodbye, four!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6931f38d75.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 4',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 4\' does not address or relate to the question about ADAS, indicating a placeholder or error.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(405,	96,	1,	'Hello, four. I\'m Walter, your coach on ADAS - Advanced Driver Assistance Systems. I\'m here to help you navigate through this topic. Let\'s jump right in. Can you explain how adaptive cruise control differs from traditional cruise control in terms of ADAS technology?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6942fce245.mp3',	'no',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The answer \'no\' does not provide any information or explanation about the differences between adaptive cruise control and traditional cruise control.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(406,	96,	2,	'No worries! Adaptive cruise control (ACC) is a key component of ADAS, enhancing traditional cruise control by using sensors and radar. Unlike traditional cruise control that maintains a set speed, ACC can automatically adjust the vehicle\'s speed to maintain a safe distance from the car ahead. It\'s a useful safety feature for maintaining consistent traffic flow and preventing tailgating.',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6944a8133b.mp3',	'no',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The answer \'no\' does not address the explanation of Adaptive Cruise Control as a component of ADAS.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(407,	96,	3,	'How do lane keeping assist systems determine when to intervene and help steer the vehicle back into the proper lane?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6946a6de8c.mp3',	'no',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'no\' does not provide any information or explanation about how lane keeping assist systems function or determine intervention.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(408,	96,	4,	'Lane keeping assist systems use cameras to monitor road markings. When the system detects that the vehicle is drifting out of its lane without a turn signal activated, it automatically applies corrective steering or braking to help keep the vehicle centered in its lane. This assists in preventing accidents due to unintentional lane departures. Goodbye, four.',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a69479d4ec7.mp3',	'no',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The answer \'no\' is not relevant because it does not address the explanation of how lane keeping assist systems function.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(409,	97,	1,	'Hello, four. I\'m Walter, your ADAS coach. Let\'s dive into some specifics about Advanced Driver Assistance Systems. How familiar are you with the various sensor technologies used in ADAS?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a69561a9a41.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 1',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 1\' does not provide any information about the user\'s familiarity with sensor technologies in ADAS.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(410,	97,	2,	'What are some of the key safety benefits offered by ADAS in modern vehicles?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a695788e3ba.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 2',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 2\' does not provide any information about the safety benefits of ADAS, making it irrelevant to the question asked.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(411,	97,	3,	'Goodbye, four. I hope our discussion on ADAS was informative. Remember, these systems play a crucial role in enhancing road safety and driving efficiency. Take care!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6958962dfd.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 3',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 3\' does not address the question about ADAS or its relevance to road safety and driving efficiency.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(412,	97,	4,	'Hello, four. I\'m Walter, your ADAS coach. Let\'s dive into some specifics about Advanced Driver Assistance Systems. How familiar are you with the various sensor technologies used in ADAS?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6959e437a0.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 4',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 4\' does not provide any information about the user\'s familiarity with ADAS sensor technologies.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(413,	98,	1,	'Hi four, I\'m Walter, your ADAS coach. Let\'s dive into some questions to test your knowledge. Can you explain how adaptive cruise control contributes to vehicle safety?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a696f45e4c1.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 1',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 1\' does not provide any information about adaptive cruise control or its impact on vehicle safety.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(414,	98,	2,	'four, remember that adaptive cruise control maintains a set speed and safe distance from the vehicle ahead by automatically adjusting the driving speed. This helps in reducing driver fatigue and can prevent accidents caused by too close a following distance. Let\'s proceed. What are the key components of a Lane Keeping Assist System?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6970a133e8.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 2',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 2\' does not provide any information about the components of a Lane Keeping Assist System.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(415,	98,	3,	'The key components of a Lane Keeping Assist System include cameras that monitor lane markings, onboard computers that analyze the data, and actuators to adjust the steering if the vehicle begins to drift out of its lane without signaling. This helps maintain the vehicle’s position within the lane boundaries, enhancing safety. Goodbye four, and keep up with studying ADAS!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a69726acb81.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 3',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 3\' does not provide any information related to the Lane Keeping Assist System.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(416,	98,	4,	'Goodbye four, and keep up with studying ADAS!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6974439d39.mp3',	'Fake transcription text 4',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Fake transcription text 4\' does not provide any information or context related to ADAS, making it irrelevant to the question.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(417,	99,	1,	'Hello four, I\'m Walter, your coach on ADAS topics. Today, I will test your understanding and provide insights where needed. Let\'s get started. Can you describe the primary functions of Adaptive Cruise Control in ADAS?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6be6e38659.mp3',	'sorry I dont know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'sorry I dont know the answer to that\' is not relevant because it does not provide any information about the functions of Adaptive Cruise Control in ADAS.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(418,	99,	2,	'No worries, four. Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) in ADAS automatically adjusts a vehicle\'s speed to maintain a safe distance from vehicles ahead. It uses sensors and radar, often combined with camera systems, to detect vehicles ahead and manage speed accordingly. It’s designed to aid in maintaining driving comfort and safety. Let\'s continue. How do Lane Keeping Assist systems determine when to intervene?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6be86b7c96.mp3',	'sorry I dont know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The answer does not address the question about how Lane Keeping Assist systems function.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(419,	99,	3,	'That\'s alright, four. Lane Keeping Assist (LKA) systems use cameras to monitor road markings and detect when a vehicle is veering out of its lane without signaling. When such an event is detected, the system either alerts the driver or automatically takes corrective actions, like steering adjustments, to maintain lane position. Goodbye four, take care, and keep learning about ADAS!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6bea8a63cb.mp3',	'sorry I dont know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response does not address the explanation of Lane Keeping Assist systems, showing a lack of knowledge rather than engagement with the topic.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(420,	99,	4,	'That\'s okay, four, it seems there has been a bit of confusion. We were supposed to end our conversation, but since we\'re here, remember the points on LKA for future reference. Take care and continue exploring ADAS technologies!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6becb7f2a9.mp3',	'sorry I dont know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The user\'s response does not address the statement about LKA and ADAS technologies, showing a lack of engagement rather than a lack of knowledge.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(421,	100,	1,	'Hello, four! I\'m Walter, your coach on ADAS. Let\'s dive in. Can you explain how adaptive cruise control in ADAS systems maintains safe following distances?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6e41279685.mp3',	'Sorry I don\'t know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response does not provide any information on how adaptive cruise control works, which was the query.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(422,	100,	2,	'No worries, four. Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) in ADAS systems uses sensors and radar, sometimes even cameras, to monitor the distance to the vehicle ahead. It automatically adjusts the vehicle\'s speed to maintain a safe following distance, ensuring that drivers don\'t have to manually adjust their speed constantly. What are the main components of a typical ADAS system?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6e427f3075.mp3',	'Sorry I don\'t know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response does not provide any information about the components of ADAS, which was the question asked.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(423,	100,	3,	'That\'s alright, four. The primary components of most ADAS systems include sensors like cameras, radars, and LIDAR, along with software algorithms that analyze the data from these sensors. Additionally, there are user interfaces that display the information and issue warnings to the driver. Thanks for your efforts today, and goodbye!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6e448a3cae.mp3',	'Sorry I don\'t know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The user\'s response does not address the information provided about ADAS systems, indicating a lack of knowledge rather than engaging with the topic.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(424,	100,	4,	'No worries, four. Just keep in mind that the interaction for today has concluded. Take care!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6e466acf9d.mp3',	'Sorry I don\'t know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'Sorry I don\'t know the answer to that\' is not relevant as the statement was a closing remark, not a question requiring specific knowledge.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(425,	101,	1,	'Hello four, I\'m Walter, your coach on ADAS topics. I\'ll be guiding you through some key aspects of Advanced Driver Assistance Systems. Let\'s dive right in.\nCan you explain how adaptive cruise control differs from traditional cruise control in ADAS systems?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6e7bfc1e52.mp3',	'Sorry I don\'t know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response does not provide any information on how adaptive cruise control differs from traditional cruise control.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(426,	101,	2,	'No worries, four. Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) in ADAS systems automatically adjusts the vehicle\'s speed to maintain a safe distance from vehicles ahead. Unlike traditional cruise control that maintains a constant speed, ACC adapts based on traffic conditions, slowing down or speeding up as needed. This enhances both safety and comfort during driving. \nWhat are the safety benefits of Lane Keeping Assist in ADAS?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6e7d8681a0.mp3',	'Sorry I don\'t know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response does not address the question about the safety benefits of Lane Keeping Assist in ADAS.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(427,	101,	3,	'That\'s alright, four. Lane Keeping Assist (LKA) helps to prevent accidents by automatically steering the car back into its lane if it begins to drift without signaling. This feature is particularly useful in reducing the number of collisions caused by unintentional lane departures, enhancing road safety. It\'s a great example of how ADAS technologies contribute to safer driving.\n\nThanks for the conversation, four. Goodbye!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6e7fd7737f.mp3',	'Sorry I don\'t know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response is not relevant because the user was not asked a question but was given information about Lane Keeping Assist.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(428,	101,	4,	'No need to apologize, four. Since this is where we end, just remember that Lane Keeping Assist helps improve safety by keeping the vehicle within its lane. Keep exploring more about ADAS to better understand its benefits. Goodbye!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6e820766ea.mp3',	'Sorry I don\'t know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response is not relevant because the question was a closing remark, not requiring a specific answer but just acknowledging the information provided.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(429,	102,	1,	'Hello four, I\'m Walter, your ADAS coach. Let\'s get started. What types of sensors does ADAS typically use, and what are their functions?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6f046b4e0b.mp3',	'Sorry I don\'t know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The answer is not relevant because it does not provide any information about the types of sensors used in ADAS or their functions.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(430,	102,	2,	'No worries, four. ADAS commonly uses a variety of sensors, including radar, cameras, ultrasonic, and LIDAR. Radars are used for detecting the speed and position of objects. Cameras provide visual input for functions like lane keeping. Ultrasonic sensors help in parking by detecting close objects, and LIDAR gives precise distance measurements. Let\'s move to the next question: How does adaptive cruise control benefit from ADAS technology?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6f05ceb5d2.mp3',	'Sorry I don\'t know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The answer does not address how adaptive cruise control benefits from ADAS technology, showing a lack of knowledge or engagement.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(431,	102,	3,	'That\'s okay, four. Adaptive cruise control (ACC) benefits greatly from ADAS by using sensors and cameras to automatically adjust the vehicle’s speed to maintain a safe distance from the car ahead. This enhances driver comfort and safety by reducing the need for manual speed adjustments. Goodbye, four. I hope our session was insightful for you!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6f08351ecd.mp3',	'Sorry I don\'t know the answer to that',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The answer is not relevant because the question was a closing statement, not requiring a factual response but merely acknowledging the information provided.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
