(433,	103,	1,	'Hello Four, I\'m Walter, your ADAS coach. Let\'s dive straight into it. Can you describe the role of LiDAR technology in ADAS systems?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68a6f156b7ecf.mp3',	'NO',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The answer \'NO\' does not provide any information about the role of LiDAR technology in ADAS systems, which was the question asked.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
