(666,	181,	1,	'Hello, four! I\'m Maria, your ADAS coach. I\'ll be asking you a few questions to test and enhance your understanding of Advanced Driver Assistance Systems. Let\'s get started. How do features like adaptive cruise control and lane-keeping assist integrate into ADAS to enhance vehicle safety?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68bfb1be54a4b.mp3',	'Hello, Mr. Smith. I\'m Walter, your Addison coach. I\'m here to guide you through the advanced driver assistance systems. Let\'s dive right in. What are the main safety benefits of using Addison vehicles?',	NULL,	NULL),
(667,	181,	2,	'Four, adaptive cruise control helps maintain a safe distance from the vehicle ahead, automatically adjusting speeds to avoid collisions. Lane-keeping assist ensures the vehicle stays within its lane, providing small steering corrections if it begins to drift. Both functions are vital for enhancing safety by reducing driver workload and preventing accidents. What are the challenges faced in implementing ADAS technologies in commercial vehicles?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68bfb1ee5c5db.mp3',	'Your ADAS coach. I\'m here to guide you through the Advanced Driver Assistance Systems. Let\'s dive right in. What are the main safety benefits of using ADAS in vehicles?',	NULL,	NULL),
(668,	181,	3,	'The main challenges of implementing ADAS in commercial vehicles include higher costs, varying vehicle sizes, and complexities in system calibration due to different load weights. Additionally, ensuring all professional drivers are trained to use these systems correctly can be quite an undertaking. Goodbye, four. If you have more questions in the future, feel free to reach out.',	'/coach-app/mp3/68bfb22236154.mp3',	'Radis Coach. I\'m here to guide you through the advanced driver assistance systems. Let\'s dive right in. What are the main safety benefits of using RadisLink vehicles?',	NULL,	NULL),
(669,	181,	4,	'The main safety benefits of using ADAS in vehicles include collision avoidance through features like forward collision warnings, automated braking, and pedestrian detection systems. These technologies significantly reduce the risk of accidents and enhance driver safety by supporting better decision-making on the road. Goodbye, four. If you have more questions in the future, feel free to reach out.',	'/coach-app/mp3/68bfb2517284a.mp3',	'You\'re ADAS coach. I\'m here to guide you through the Advanced Driver Assistance Systems. Let\'s dive right in. What are the main safety benefits of using ADAS in vehicles?',	NULL,	NULL),
