(674,	194,	1,	'Hello four, I\'m Maria, your coach on ADAS. Let\'s dive into some details to enhance your understanding. How do lane departure warning systems detect lane markings on the road?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68c12b5b8e7c1.mp3',	'My automated answer for interaction 1',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'My automated answer for interaction 1\' does not address the question about how lane departure warning systems detect lane markings.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(675,	194,	2,	'Lane departure warning systems typically use cameras mounted near the rearview mirror to monitor lane markings. By analyzing the captured images, the system can detect when the vehicle begins to drift out of its lane without signaling, prompting an alert to the driver. This helps in maintaining the vehicle\'s position on the road. What are the typical sensors used in adaptive cruise control systems, and how do they function?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68c12b627b3f0.mp3',	'My automated answer for interaction 2',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'My automated answer for interaction 2\' does not address the question about sensors in adaptive cruise control systems.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(676,	194,	3,	'Adaptive cruise control systems usually rely on radar and sometimes lidar sensors to gauge the distance from vehicles ahead. These sensors emit signals that bounce back after hitting an object, measuring the time taken to return to determine the distance. This allows the system to adjust the vehicle\'s speed accordingly to maintain a safe following distance. Goodbye, four, and take care!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68c12b6c3d56b.mp3',	'My automated answer for interaction 3',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The user\'s response does not address the question about adaptive cruise control systems; it merely repeats a phrase unrelated to the query.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
(677,	194,	4,	'It appears there\'s a misunderstanding, four. This is the end of our session on ADAS. If you have further questions in the future, feel free to explore more about the topic. Take care and goodbye!',	'/coach-app/mp3/68c12b757d092.mp3',	'My automated answer for interaction 4',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'My automated answer for interaction 4\' does not address the question about ADAS, showing a lack of relevance.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
