(680,	195,	3,	'Four, that\'s quite right! ADAS systems commonly utilize radar, cameras, and ultrasonic sensors. How do these sensors contribute to the functionality of systems like adaptive cruise control or lane keeping assistance?',	'/coach-app/mp3/68c12bda19a69.mp3',	'My automated answer for interaction 3',	NULL,	'<br>\r\n<b>Was the answer relevant?</b>: no\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Why?</b>: The response \'My automated answer for interaction 3\' does not address how sensors contribute to ADAS functionalities.\r\n<br>\r\n<b>Score:</b>: 0 pts / 5 pts<br><br>'),
